# <Disease Or Finding Name> Disease Chapter Research Plan

Use this search and review plan before writing or materially revising a
`clinical-statistical-expert` disease chapter.

The goal is not to produce a systematic review. The goal is to read enough
authoritative clinical and imaging material to write a safe, useful, source-
grounded disease chapter for research planning, cohort definition, imaging
review, and statistical interpretation.

